  "desc": "Wielders of abyssal fire who pursue the meaning behind texts and scriptures. Is a member of the Abyss Order.<br/>The surface people have a slightly distorted understanding of what their name means, calling them \"Lectors,\" when their name can also mean \"exegete.\" Reading the word of grace grants them great power.",
